    "en": {
      "name": "Legendary Klesha Six Samurai - Enishi",
      "effect": "1 Tuner + 1+ non-Tuner monsters\nWarrior monsters you control gain 500 ATK/DEF during the Battle Phase only. You can only use each of the following effects of \"Legendary Klesha Six Samurai - Enishi\" once per turn. If this card is Synchro Summoned: You can banish any number of \"Six Samurai\" monsters from your GY, then target that many monsters your opponent controls; return them to the hand. If this card is sent to the GY: You can Special Summon 1 of your banished \"Six Samurai\" monsters.",
      "official": false
    },
